Really tasty salad. Two slices of proscuitto worked perfectly. Followed the recipe except I made my own vinaigrette since I didn't have pomegranate vinegar: 1T pomegranate juice, 1T white balsamic vinegar, 1/4 cup olive oil, 1 crushed garlic clove, 1/4t salt.

