Rating: 4
We loved this salad....but we didn't have it as a salad. Rather, we toasted baguette slices. Then we made the "salad" by starting with diced persimmon and then adding chopped arugula and all remaining ingredients in proportion until things seemed balanced. Then we spooned the diced mixed salad on the baguette toasts and served the salad as bruschetta. It was yummy.

